{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"67b1e3ee5d","title":"集中全力歼灭机疲之敌","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"40608e2893","index":0,"year":1936,"month":11,"day":3,"articleId":"67b1e3ee5d"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji9-1","name":"毛泽东全集第9卷(1)","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji9-1.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji9-1":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"59490def93","type":"paragraph","text":"集中全力歼灭机疲之敌！","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"67b1e3ee5d"},{"id":"5ae6d0c301","type":"paragraph","text":"（1936年11月3日）各首长：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"67b1e3ee5d"},{"id":"fc9028b6e7","type":"paragraph","text":"关麟征称：率师近日以来星夜追，所过之地给养万分困难，官兵日夜不得一餐，现已夹失靖远、打拉池一带，给养仍日不得饱等语。以情势观察，不独关师，追敌各部当有相同困难，目前敌疲备已达最高度。宜以此特别情况激励士气，集中全力消灭敌人，争取全战役之胜利","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"67b1e3ee5d"},{"id":"b61680e5b7","type":"paragraph","text":"毛周[I]这是毛泽东和周恩来给红军各部队首长的电报。","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"67b1e3ee5d"},{"id":"bfa342ef75","type":"paragraph","text":"2关麟征，当时任国民党军西北“”总司令部第三路第十一纵队司令兼第二十五师师长。","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"67b1e3ee5d"}],"page":{"id":"f20de3cc36","publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"67b1e3ee5d","start":277,"end":277}}}},"__N_SSG":true}